      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ARK SEA (3) has had a let-up since leading throughout last start at Menangle but was kept up to the mark with a trial win. The only time she has been beaten in four starts this campaign was when she came from the outside barrier for fifth in the NSW Oaks. Has the speed to take advantage of this draw and won the only time she raced here. The one to beat. MESSAGE BANK (9) was a beaten favourite when fourth here last time out but loves this distance, winning six of nine attempts. No harm in drawing here with the sprint lane to rely upon. Should play  role. SNAP SHOT NZ (5) drops back in grade off Listed level but was a winner at Menangle prior and scored last time she raced here so looms as a challenger. NOVANTA RISING (1) is building in fitness and draws to advantage.",
